```plantuml
@startuml hyeonsangjeon_AWS-LLM-SageMaker

actor User
participant "Streamlit UI" as UI
participant "RAG Controller" as Controller
participant "OpenSearch" as OS
participant "SageMaker Endpoint\n(LLM)" as LLM
participant "Embedding Model" as Embed

User -> UI: Submits financial question
UI -> Controller: Forward question
Controller -> Embed: Generate embedding for question
Embed --> Controller: Return question vector
Controller -> OS: Search with question vector
OS --> Controller: Return relevant document chunks
Controller -> LLM: Generate answer with\nquestion + documents
LLM --> Controller: Return generated answer
Controller -> UI: Display answer
UI -> User: Show response

@enduml
```